Scorponok looks thoughtful at the womens response, then cries over to
Sharpclaws, "Keep youre chassis on. Very well ladies, I will give you a
chance, after all" he smile but is it warm or sinister? " It's the least I
can do." He says almost unsure of himself "But I am not promising you my
future, i'm only  giving youre group a chance, there is little I know of
what is going on" He then looks to Terrosaur's form "Blast it" He yells
"It's just an exoskeleton not the real thing, how could I make that
mistake" he then starts to stumble, "Beast Mode" While transforming to
beast mode though the wheels that he noticed earlier come into effect and
Adjust with him until he is a race car "What the slag" He stammers"
